physical_examinations.relevant_findings: The patient had a SynchroMed EL Infusion Pump in place for chronic pain management, with reported discrepancies in aspirated and calculated residual volumes (aspirated: 1.0 ml, expected: 7.6 ml)
physical_examinations.changes_over_time: The patient's condition warranted further evaluation due to a lack of CSF back-flow, culminating in the discovery of an intrathecal catheter-tip mass confirmed by MRI.
